query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `quiz_responses` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `sessionId` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `answers` text NOT NULL,
  `recommendedPlan` varchar(100),
  `score` int,
  `profile` varchar(100),
  `studentCount` varchar(50),
  `revenue` varchar(50),
  `lostInfo` varchar(50),
  `adminTime` varchar(50),
  `churn` varchar(50),
  `billingIssues` varchar(50),
  `mainGoal` varchar(100),
  `completedAt` timestamp,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
  `source` varchar(100),
  `utmSource` varchar(255),
  `utmMedium` varchar(255),
  `utmCampaign` varchar(255),
  `utmContent` varchar(255),
  `utmTerm` varchar(255),
  `referrer` varchar(500),
  `userAgent` text,
  `ipAddress` varchar(100),
  `deviceType` varchar(50),
  `browser` varchar(100),
  `os` varchar(100),
  `screenResolution` varchar(50),
  `language` varchar(20),
  `timezone` varchar(100),
  `country` varchar(100),
  `city` varchar(100),
  `converted` boolean DEFAULT false,
  `convertedAt` timestamp,
  `conversionType` varchar(50),
  `personalId` int,
  `notes` text,
  CONSTRAINT `quiz_responses_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);
